{"tid":1442152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭政府同黑警用無間計, 我地點解唔可以用","createTime":"2019-08-11T00:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T01:14:35.000Z","uid":125079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2072a393c1c86363501e5ac18209da9219337c2","tid":1442152,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"黑警換黑衫扮示威者 然後乘機捉人<br />\n<br />\n有人扮示威者四處辱罵人破壞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">依加班大陸豬係微博仲要屈721班白衫人係示威者扮黎襲擊市民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點解我地唔可以學佢地依種方法? </span></span><br />\n<br />\n簡單如平時網上扮藍絲, 融入藍屍群拎資料<br />\n<br />\n今日又有福建獨立黎, 如果有福建人周圍破壞, 貼野, 阻住人做生意會點? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n福建人今日講到明要教訓香港人, 成個北角今日一定變禁區, 冇居民敢出黎<br />\n<br />\n班福建人/黑社會係黎破壞香港經濟, 唔洗正面打, 佢地班死蠢落多啲黎香港, 去曬唔同區, 包保區區宵禁<br />\n<br />\n大家話要唔購物, 進行經濟示威比林鄭壓力, 班大陸人同黑社會其實已幫我地做緊野, 佢地去到邊, 個區一定冇人敢出出黎"},{"pid":"0b9f88006fa17a9f45d369dc45f10a6594286283","tid":1442152,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭記招篩選傳媒  經濟問題優先  我覺得記者可以咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d7e4080c3879443bcf51b79dc08a5634743b276","tid":1442152,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每一次都係比人屈 <br />\n<br />\n黑社會同黑警不停做25仔混入黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9943248c29162fcdd8392ed13f4f68fd0611f3ea","tid":1442152,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" clas